---
title: Quick Korean Beef Stir-Fry Noodles with Asian Veggies, Fried Egg & Peanuts
description: Sometimes you can’t go past the classics, like this Korean-style beef stir-fry. It feels like a bibimbap that we all know and love, except
with a little twist of swapping rice for udon noodles. Add some colourful veggies, a fried egg and peanuts and it'll start tasting like a
takeaway delight, but with the satisfaction of making it yourself!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-korean-beef-stir-fry-noodles-570b051a.jpg
